4 IC 35-38-1-9, IC 35-38-1-12, and IC 35-38-1-17, and IC 35-40-5-5,
5 means a person who has suffered harm as a result of a crime.
6 (b) "Victim", for purposes of IC 35-37-6, has the meaning set forth
7 in IC 35-37-6-3.
8 (c) "Victim", for purposes of IC 35-38-7, has the meaning set forth
9 in IC 35-38-7-4.
10 (d) "Victim", for purposes of IC 35-40, except for IC 35-40-5-5,
11 has the meaning set forth in IC 35-40-4-8.
12 (e) "Victim", for purposes of IC 35-40.5 has the meaning set forth
